column5: Two bodies pulled from car in Niagara River in Fort Erie....  http://www.buffalonews.com/city/communities/southern-ontario/article834044.ece
Now that's terrible. The water isn't very deep there, its a shallow ramp. Its mind boggling why the occupants couldn't have gotten out.
How do you miss that stop and caution sign??  They must have been moving.
Could be a DUI as well. Guess it will be known when the autopsies are done.
